{"tid":1083945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環去觀塘只需五毫？！","createTime":"2019-03-30T04:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T04:45:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"767e44d9f9cdff1628515b263654c23b65b3e581","tid":1083945,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xi4N3ms.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxi4N3ms.png&h=e755372a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c536b2db1a510fc2c88a04a7f17ef7bdf79b303a","tid":1083945,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"1980年，地鐵公司為方便經常乘搭地鐵的乘客，推出了地鐵多程票，與單程票一樣，採用有磁帶的膠質車票，票值用完後，會被出閘機收回。1981年，推出更具彈性的地鐵儲值票，取代地鐵多程票。<br />\n<br />\n1984年10月15日，九廣鐵路票務系統自動化，地鐵儲值票亦適用於紅磡至上水各站，並由當時兩鐵經理於九龍塘站舉行儀式。這種車票便改由地鐵與九鐵聯合發行，並命名為通用儲值票。<br />\n<br />\n其後九巴及城巴的 M線接駁巴士也適用於通用儲值票，當時好多人用剩幾毫甚至一毫，就儲起等搭巴士或地鐵過海，而使用儲值票須知，就是切勿接近磁石，因為吸了裡面的磁粉，就等於吸錢。<br />\n<br />\n1999年1月2日，隨著具有多重用途的八達通普及，通用儲值票停用。<br />\n<br />\n報章來自1981年3月30日星期一「華僑日報」"},{"pid":"fc950b3c526c907e227fc815ad5729cb7fdbf422","tid":1083945,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"我話ok就ok ，冇特別野我返去打golf"},{"pid":"18d1cd462e30d9568e146add3a163e34492192e5","tid":1083945,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tpTSu3m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtpTSu3m.png&h=f30721eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4996043e2c237be8c16f4c285fbe47751fa27237","tid":1083945,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LNJi94G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLNJi94G.png&h=31aa43f5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}